@page "/calculators"

<PageTitle>Calculators</PageTitle>

<h1>Calculators</h1>
<p class="lead">
    A curated set of helpers focused on clarity and discoverability. Each calculator is documented
    with inputs, formulas, and output expectations.
</p>

<div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Loan amortization</p>
        <p class="card-text">Monthly payment schedule, total interest, and payoff dates.</p>
        <span class="tag">Finance</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Unit conversion</p>
        <p class="card-text">Length, area, and volume conversions with sensible defaults.</p>
        <span class="tag">Utilities</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Energy usage</p>
        <p class="card-text">Estimate consumption and costs from wattage and runtime.</p>
        <span class="tag">Engineering</span>
    </div>
</div>

<h2>Planned formulas</h2>
<table>
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>Calculator</th>
        <th>Formula</th>
        <th>Output</th>
    </tr>
